<F P=100> BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Muslim Snipers Kill 2 Civilians in Doboj Area </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0803200094 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1923 GMT 8 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0803200094 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Doboj, 8 Mar (TANJUG)--Muslim snipers today 
killed two civilians in Serb villages on the right bank of the 
River Bosna, the information service of the Srpska republic 
army's 1st Krajina corps has reported. 
  The statement says that the Muslim forces were firing at the 
Serb positions with small arms and mortars along most 
demarcation lines in the wider area of Doboj. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

