<H3> <TI>   Tuchyna on Cabinet's Work on Border Settlements </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD083173694 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network 
in Slovak 1100 GMT 8 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD083173694 </F>
<F P=104>  Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network 
in Slovak 1100 GMT 8 Mar 94 </F>



