  [Text] Sofia, March 8 (BTA) -- Prime Minister Lyuben Berov 
had a heart failure at 2 AM [0000 GMT] on March 8, the Cabinet 
Press Office said today. He was taken to the Lozenets Hospital 
of the Military Medical Academy in Sofia. A team held 
