<H3> <TI>   Cabinet Meets Briefly, Postpones Agenda Items </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1003093894 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 0900 
GMT 10 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1003093894 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Bulgarian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The regular meeting of the cabinet today lasted less 
than an hour. The cabinet adopted the regulations for the 
activity of the Interdepartmental Committee on Priority 
Environmental Projects and the Development of the Republic of 
Bulgaria. The draft agreements for trade-economic cooperation 
with Armenia, Azerbaijan, and Uzbekistan, and an agreement on 
the mutual protection of investments with Poland, also were 
adopted. 
