<F P=100> BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Serb Attack Kills Seven in Bihac, Maglaj </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1003084194 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 0700 GMT 10 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1003084194 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The region of Bihac remains the focus of aggressor's 
offensive. Throughout yesterday the aggressor used howitzers, 
in particular, and tanks to pound the area. Three civilians 
were killed and dozens injured. The aggressor also attacked the 
defense lines and threatened the Bihac-Cazin road. Forces of 
the so-called "autonomasi" [anti-Izetbegovic forces] have been 
also been very active. 
  Attacks on Maglaj were of a slightly lesser ferocity but 
there were civilian fatalities nevertheless. Chetnik snipers, 
howitzers and mortars killed four civilians. Infantry attacks 
were repulsed. The humanitarian situation in the town is 
exceptionally difficult. 

</TEXT>

