<H3> <TI>   Redman, Izetbegovic, Delic Discuss Accord </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0903193994 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 1800 GMT 9 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0903193994 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Today Alija Izetbegovic, president of the 
Bosnia-Herzegovina Presidency, received Mr. Charles Redman, 
special envoy of Bill Clinton, and General (Galvin), special 
envoy for military affairs. 
  The meeting was also attended by Bosnia-Herzegovina Army 
Commander General Delic. They discussed the possibilities for 
the implementation of the agreement between the 
Bosnia-Herzegovina Army and the Croatian Defense Council, on 
which General (Galvin) and his team will offer their assistance. 

