<F P=100> BULGARIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Prime Minister Undergoes Heart Bypass Surgery </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1103103094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1000 
GMT 11 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1103103094 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Bulgarian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Government spokesman Raycho Raykov is on the line. 
Good Day Mr. Raykov, we have heard that the prime minister is 
being operated on at the moment. 
  [Raykov] Yes, it appears your information is correct. This 
morning the medical team at the Lozenets Hospital of the 
Military-Medical Academy, where Prime Minister Berov is 
hospitalized, decided to perform a bypass operation. We expect 
the operation to end in about one hour. When the results of the 
operation become clear the Press Center will issue an official 
announcement. 
  [Announcer] We will expect your announcement. 

</TEXT>

