<F P=102>  AU1003204194 Paris AFP in English 2039 GMT 10 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU1003204194 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Zagreb, March 10 (AFP)--Bosnian Croats said Thursday 
[10 March] they would not accept a federation with Moslems in 
Bosnia-Herzegovina which was not linked to a confederation with 
Croatia proper. 
  A statement said: ``The presidential council has decided 
that 
setting up a federation is conditional on the establishment of a 
confederation between the Republic of Croatia and the federation 
of Bosnia-Herzegovina. 
  "That means that a federation cannot be established without 
the setting up of a confederation." 

