<H3> <TI>   Swiss Branch of PDP To Meet Unpaid Debt </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1303205694 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1900 
GMT 13 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1303205694 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Presidency of the Party for Democratic 
Prosperity [PDP] branch in Switzerland reports that in a meeting 
in Zurich on 12 March, the presidency decided that this party 
branch will meet a part of the unpaid obligation of the Albanian 
population in the former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia 
concerning the investments for the satellite program project. 
  This branch will ensure a sum of 300,000 Swiss francs until 
1 
May 1994. The money will be deposited in the account of the 
satellite program of the Albanian Radio-Television. 

