Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Council of Ministers Press Center has announced 
that according to information supplied by the medical team 
treating Prime Minister Lyuben Berov, the team made an extended 
visit to their patient at about 1800 hours this afternoon, with 
the surgeons Prof. Levi and Docent Mishev also in attendance. 
